{
  "style": "IEEE",
  "texts": [
    "However, communicational tools like ChatGPT and other GenAI tools are less prevalent in industrial operational manufacturing areas [20].We exploit the benefits of generative AI and ChatGPT to the advantage of a small experimental manufacturing factory by designing a GPT industrial bot, available in two versions offline and online, that improves factory operators' daily working experience by the following:• Closely monitor factory production and incorporate essential parameters such as plant pollution level and maximum overtime working hours to keep factory operations decision-making safe for workers and their environment.",
    "• Assisting workers in finding faults for accessible equipment, root cause analysis, and synthetic data generation using text queries.",
    "• Increasing operators' work knowledge and understanding with additional information and tips related to every query received thanks to the OpenAI GPT4 database (this feature is mainly available in the online bot version).We generate the online industrial bot version by configuring the customized GPT functionality in the GPT4.0 LM platform to match a small to medium-sized manufacturing environment and learn about customized factory data.",
    "For the offline version, we integrate the GPT4.0 LM via OpenAI APIs in the backend of a chatbot designed with Streamlit, a Python-compatible web-based visualization tool, for the front end.Our research investigates a new approach for human-tomachine interaction in an I5.0 context for production monitoring, system troubleshooting, and synthetic data generation in small factories.",
    "Unlike in previous industrial revolutions, where operators predominantly interact with production machines via human-machine interfaces (HMI) and supervisory control and data acquisition (SCADA) systems, our study suggests an industrial chatbot as the interaction media."
  ],
  "correct_citations": [
    "However, communicational tools like ChatGPT and other GenAI tools are less prevalent in industrial operational manufacturing areas [20].We exploit the benefits of generative AI and ChatGPT to the advantage of a small experimental manufacturing factory by designing a GPT industrial bot, available in two versions offline and online, that improves factory operators' daily working experience by the following:• Closely monitor factory production and incorporate essential parameters such as plant pollution level and maximum overtime working hours to keep factory operations decision-making safe for workers and their environment."
  ]
}